data.description: Spacious 2-story home located the highly desirable east side. This 4-bedroom home boasts 2 1/2 baths, with all the bedrooms conveniently located upstairs and 2 living areas. Upon entering, you are greeted by a formal living area followed by an open kitchen, featuring granite countertops, crown molding cabinets, and a spacious island. The adjoining dining area provides ample space perfect for entertaining. The master bedroom includes a separate space that can easily be transformed into a nursery, reading room, or home office. The master bathroom features double sinks, a separate shower area, and a walk-in closet. The remaining bedrooms are generously sized and come with wall-to-wall closets or walk-in closets. Laundry room is conveniently located upstairs. Additional features include an amazing MOVIE THEATER downstairs, two-car garage and a good-sized yard with cement areas and walkways, offering endless possibilities for landscaping and outdoor activities. Schedule a showing today!
